    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chicken thighs</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) (use <strong>tin foil </strong>to avoid mess!) and drizzle over the <strong>honey mustard marinade</strong>, then<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 17-18 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>baked honey mustard chicken</strong></p>",
