      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken and quinoa are cooking, chop your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
