    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>sliced shallot</strong> and the <strong>lemon zest</strong> to a large bowl</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style salad</strong></p>",
