    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the quinoa is cooked, add the<strong> chopped parsley </strong>and <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and stir everything together – this is your <strong>Mediterranean-style quinoa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>into wedges</p>",
